{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7b3dc3355d","title":"右派言论——攻击社会主义制度","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3e8ecf48e5","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"7b3dc3355d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1d435fc3ef","name":"姚铁奎"},{"id":"1fbe7fb5f1","name":"李启文"},{"id":"443b955d0a","name":"杜贵圈"},{"id":"6c72d91291","name":"河南农学院"},{"id":"b70caf6787","name":"姜卓廉"},{"id":"ecb0498155","name":"黄纪斌"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b787db62a8","type":"title","text":"右派言论——攻击社会主义制度","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"},{"id":"41ab8bfe52","type":"authors","text":"河南农学院姚铁奎黄纪斌杜贵圈李启文姜卓廉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"},{"id":"0a5c592a51","type":"paragraph","text":"姚铁奎（理化教研组讲师）：进入社会主义几天了，还能买不到冰（注：指新社会冷酷如冰）。孩子死了好，不然将来也是饿死。社会主义建设的百年大计，就似大楼裂缝。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"},{"id":"fd4e51a744","type":"paragraph","text":"黄纪斌（农59级学生，党员）：新社会使人乏味，人与人的关系是人心危危，不可相信。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"},{"id":"3e5dfa5956","type":"paragraph","text":"杜贵圈（农60级学生）：各民主党派可以轮流执政，因为你（注：指共产党）有一个方向，谁都可以照着执行，好像学校的教学计划，院长或副院长都可贯彻一样。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"},{"id":"a336bb5eee","type":"paragraph","text":"李启文（农59级学生）：社会主义制度是产生教条主义的根源。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"},{"id":"a4dbb10129","type":"paragraph","text":"姜卓廉（农60级学生，院学生会副主席）：根据质量互变定律，社会主义制度也要灭亡。明明农民生活很苦，为什么说不苦，这种不实事求是的说法，必须坚决反对。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"},{"id":"33613f4a9b","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选辑》（河南农学院，1957年12月）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d"}],"page":{"id":"9a6b7fb1ad","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7b3dc3355d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}